<paragraph id="32EFA8614943A75F0251BA0B3DA1CFEF" pageId="11" pageNumber="12">Material examined.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="DBA637FE1F12CB340FADEFC24191F85E" pageId="11" pageNumber="12">Type specimen: HolotypeZMA Por. 22412, encrusting a stone, preserved in alcohol.</paragraph>
