, 
<geoCoordinate id="E4498F9C98B0EAD3E2756AF8EF084C57" direction="west" orientation="longitude" precision="5" value="-16.4167">16.4167°W</geoCoordinate>
, on sandstone ridge, dredged, 12-18 m. coll. R.W.M. van Soest &amp; J.J. Vermeulen, Mauritania II Exped. Stat. 49, 11
